title: So I Went On Bear Grylls And THIS Happened!
description:
Here is my conversation with Bear Grylls, where we discussed my upcoming appearance on "Running Wild with Bear Grylls: The Challenge". We talked about my terror and discomfort during the filming of the show, how Bear grounds himself in today's world, and much more... #beargrylls #survival #nationalgeographic 

Check out my episode Sunday 6th August on National Geographic.
